## Description {#details}

A <a href="/docs/api/structs/livedebugvalues/dbgop">DbgOp</a> whose <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/callingconv/#abdf8cf606905c10634e831390981b0ed">ID</a> (if any) has resolved to an actual location, <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/locidx">LocIdx</a>.

Used when working with concrete debug values, i.e. when joining MLocs and VLocs in the <a href="/docs/api/classes/transfertracker">TransferTracker</a> or emitting DBG&#95;VALUE/DBG&#95;VALUE&#95;LIST instructions in the <a href="/docs/api/classes/livedebugvalues/mloctracker">MLocTracker</a>.
